          <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>ADDENDUM FOR DEFERRED PAYMENT SOLUTIONS </strong></span></p>

<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>
<p>Dear Merchant,</p>

<p><strong>Re: <u>Availing Deferred Payment Solutions Enabled by PayU</u></strong></p>
<p><strong><u>&nbsp;</u></strong></p>
<table cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="border-collapse: collapse;">
                    <tr>
                        <td valign="top">1.</td>
                        <td>We refer to the service agreement entered into between PayU Payments Private Limited (&quot;<strong>PayU</strong>&quot;) and You (&quot;<strong>Service Agreement</strong>&quot;) pursuant to which PayU has been providing aggregate online payment gateway solutions and services to You.</td> 
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td valign="top">2.</td>
                        <td>PayU has entered into certain arrangements with Partner Financial Institution(s) (as defined in the Deferred Payment Solutions T&amp;Cs) pursuant to which PayU can enable an option for Your Customers for availing Deferred Payment Solutions (as defined in the Deferred Payment Solutions T&amp;Cs) that are made available by the aforesaid Partner Financial Institution(s) for making payments against the purchase of Products.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td valign="top">3.</td>
                        <td >The aforesaid Deferred Payment Solutions by PayU are being offered to the Merchant in accordance with the terms and conditions available at <a href="https://payu.in/deferred-payment-solutions-tnc">https://payu.in/deferred-payment-&nbsp;solutions-tnc</a> ("<strong>Deferred Payment Solutions</strong><strong> T&amp;Cs</strong>").</td>   
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td valign="top">4.</td>
                        <td >The Merchant agrees to pay Service Fee to PayU for availing Deferred Payment Solutions, as advised by PayU from time to time and with regard to the two Deferred Payment Solutions as provided in the table below, the following Service Fee will be applicable:</td>   
                    </tr>
